# Sponsor logos go in this directory.
#
# File naming: use the sponsor's `id` from _data/sponsors.yml.
# Example: _data/sponsors.yml entry with `id: acme-security` looks for
#          assets/images/sponsors/acme-security.png (or .svg).
#
# Format recommendations:
#   - PNG with transparent background, OR SVG
#   - Footer site-sponsor logos render at 28px tall (max-width auto)
#   - Per-report banner logos render at 20px tall
#   - Provide a logo at least 2x display size (56px tall PNG) for retina
